## THE THESIS\
\
**AI handles 70% of the work (orchestration, coaching, matching, tracking, facilitation). Human peer accountability delivers the 30% that actually drives behavior change.** This is not an AI coaching app. This is not a community. This is an AI-powered accountability *engine* that makes structured human peer groups work at scale \'97 without human facilitators.\
