### Why Each Competitor Can't Easily Copy You\
\
**ChatGPT / Claude / Gemini:** Can provide 1-on-1 AI coaching but cannot create peer squads, social pressure, or scheduled human accountability appointments. The group dynamic is structurally impossible in a chat interface.\
