1. **Squad social bonds** \'97 Once people form real relationships in their squad, switching costs are enormous. This is the strongest moat.\
2. **Behavioral data flywheel** \'97 Every sprint generates data on what goal types, squad compositions, check-in frequencies, and coaching interventions produce the best outcomes. This makes your matching and facilitation AI better over time. Competitors starting from scratch can't replicate years of cohort data.\
