## PART 6: PRODUCT ARCHITECTURE \'97 WHAT TO BUILD\
\
### The AI Agent Stack\
\
Your competitive advantage is that you build AI agents. Here's how they map to this product:\
\
**Agent 1: The Matchmaker**\
- Intake questionnaire data \uc0\u8594  squad matching algorithm\
- Factors: timezone, goal type (business/personal/spiritual), personality balance, experience level\
- Runs every sprint cycle to form or reform squads\
- Improves over time using retention and satisfaction data\
\
**Agent 2: The Sprint Facilitator**\
- Runs the entire 6-week sprint rhythm automatically\
- Monday: Sends goal-setting prompts, collects declarations, shares with squad\
- Wednesday: Sends status check prompts (Green/Yellow/Red), surfaces blockers\
- Friday: Facilitates reflection, celebrates wins, extracts learnings\
- Week 3: Triggers "Dip Intervention" \'97 motivation reset, goal adjustment amnesty\
- Week 6: Runs retrospective, triggers squad vote for continuation or reshuffle\
\
**Agent 3: The Personal Coach**\
- 1-on-1 AI conversations for goal refinement, obstacle analysis, mindset support\
- Has full context of the user's sprint history, goal completion rates, patterns\
- Provides personalized insights: "You've missed Wednesday check-ins 3 sprints in a row \'97 your mid-week engagement predicts lower goal completion. Here's what I'd suggest..."\
- Available 24/7 between human check-in points\
\
**Agent 4: The Engagement Guardian**\
- Monitors all squad activity\
- Detects disengagement patterns (missed check-ins, declining message length, silent days)\
- Triggers "Life Check" DMs (your Oumafy "Pause Protocol")\
- Alerts you (the founder) when a squad is at risk of collapse\
- Manages the pause/resume flow without squad disruption\
\
**Agent 5: The Analytics Engine**\
- Tracks per-user and per-squad metrics: goal completion rate, attendance, engagement score\
- Generates weekly squad health dashboards\
- Produces "Sprint Report Cards" at the end of each cycle\
- Feeds data back into the Matchmaker for better future squad composition\
- Generates retention predictions: "This user has a 72% chance of churning after this sprint"\
